<h1>Pills</h1>

<p>Pills are comenly used to display tags or inline statuses. They are usually colored to reflect their content.</p>

<h2>Simple Usage</h2>

<p>Let's look at a basic example of a pill.</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="pill" class="uxs"}}

    {{#uxs-div class="clear"}}
      {{uxs-pill text style=style size=size rounded=rounded}}
      {{uxs-pill "primary" style="primary" size=size rounded=rounded}}
      {{uxs-pill "accent" style="accent" size=size rounded=rounded}}
      {{uxs-pill "warning" style="warning" size=size rounded=rounded}}
      {{uxs-pill "error" style="error" size=size rounded=rounded}}
    {{/uxs-div}}

  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet "pill.hbs"}}

{{/docs-demo}}

